Origin:

    https://github.com/davidosomething/dotfiles/blob/master/zsh/.zshrc
    https://github.com/davidosomething/dotfiles/blob/master/zsh/zinit.zsh

but highly shortened when narrowing to find bugs, now basically a syntetic test
that stresses out support for commands leading zinit in following way: "foo
&& zinit ..." and similar, especially at the beginning of zinit block, and
even more at the beginning of whole zshrc.
